data.description: The Oaks offers a perfect location for buyers who want to be close to everything St Charles offers, but love the close proximity to Geneva too. Enjoy great restaurants and biking and walking trails along the Fox River and Mt St Mary's park. 10 Roosevelt is a 3 bed/2.1 bath townhome, with separate living and dining rooms. The kitchen has nice storage and counter space, newer range and microwave. The family room, with gas fireplace, is currently used as an eating space but can easily be a family room with plenty of room to gather. The outdoor brick paver patio is just off the kitchen. Enjoy shade and open space, while grilling and relaxing. Three nicely sized bedrooms, including a primary bedroom with attached bath and walk in closet. Seller uses the second bedroom as a home office. Bedrooms two and three share a full bath. The unfinished basement is clean and dry with an abundance of storage. HWH 2023, all windows replaced 2017/2019. Be sure to notice the two car garage and private yard space. A buyer with a green thumb can enjoy gardening in the private garden area off the front entrance. The private clubhouse and pool are enjoyed by residents, be sure to check them out during your showing. Welcome home.
